     Part 2: Sidecar Process (lb/sidecar/src/)

     2.1 health_check.ts (NEW) — Interface

     interface HealthCheck {
       isHealthy(): boolean;
       getDrainInterval(): number;  // ms, default 200
     }

     2.2 always_healthy.ts (NEW)

     - AlwaysHealthy implements HealthCheck
     - isHealthy() → true
     - getDrainInterval() → 200

     2.3 health_check_runner.ts (NEW)

     - HealthCheckRunner extends EventEmitter
     - Runs all checks on a setInterval (default 1ms)
     - healthy: all checks pass; drainInterval: max of all getDrainInterval()
     - Emits stateChange event on healthy↔unhealthy transitions

     2.4 lb_connection.ts (NEW)

     - LbConnection class — TCP client to load balancer
     - connect() / disconnect() lifecycle
     - sendDrain(durationMs): writes DRAIN:<ms>\n
     - sendResume(): writes RESUME\n
     - Auto-reconnect on connection loss with capped exponential backoff

     2.5 config.ts (NEW)

     - SidecarConfig: lbHost, lbPort, checkIntervalMs (default 1), metricsPort, healthChecks: string[]
     - loadSidecarConfig(filePath) — YAML parsing + validation

     2.6 metrics_server.ts (NEW)

     - Simple HTTP server on metricsPort
     - GET /metrics returns OpenTelemetry text format:
     # HELP sidecar_server_healthy Whether the monitored server is healthy
     # TYPE sidecar_server_healthy gauge
     sidecar_server_healthy 1

     2.7 health_check_factory.ts (NEW)

     - createHealthChecks(names: string[]): HealthCheck[]
     - Maps "always_healthy" → new AlwaysHealthy()
     - Throws on unknown names (extensible for future checks)

     2.8 sidecar.ts (NEW) — Orchestrator

     - Sidecar class wires together runner, connection, metrics server
     - Redundant send loop: sends DRAIN or RESUME every drainInterval / 2 (minimum 50ms)
     - Also sends immediately on state change
     - start() / stop() lifecycle

     2.9 main.ts (NEW) — Entry point

     - Loads config from CLI arg / SIDECAR_CONFIG_PATH env / default
     - Creates health checks via factory
     - Creates and starts Sidecar
     - Graceful shutdown on SIGINT/SIGTERM

     2.10 index.ts (NEW) — Re-exports

     2.11 package.json (MODIFY)

     - Add js-yaml, @types/js-yaml, @types/node dependencies

     2.12 Tests

     - always_healthy.test.ts
     - health_check_runner.test.ts — state transitions, drainInterval calculation
     - lb_connection.test.ts — mock TCP server integration

